name: Senior #25 - Ethel
description:
Ethel is a 62-year-old senior cashier at a local grocer who enjoys tv dinner, paid charity work, and preaching to kids who are going through puberty. She is generous and giving, but can also be very loud-mouthed and judgemental.

Ethel’s best friend is a laundromat owner called Patricia. They have an extreme love-hate friendship. Every Friday evening they hang out at Ethel’s place to watch Jeopardy! while having their favorite all natural tv dinner.
